cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.CG, cs.SI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with the development of a new second-generation curvelet transform on the sphere, which is a signal processing technique. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories.
